<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.9">
<l>maḻuṅkāta vainnutiya cakkaranal valattaiyāy</l>
<l>toḻuṅkātal kaḷiṟaḷippāṉ puḷḷūrntu tōṉṟiṉaiyē</l>
<l>maḻuṅkāta ñāṉamē paṭaiyāka malarulakiṟ</l>
<l>ṟoḻumpāyārk kaḷittāluṉ cuṭarccōti maṟaiyātē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the discus in [your] sharp nails that do not become blunt you appeared,</l>
<l>mounted on the bird in order to provide for the loving elephant who worshipped [you] as good treasure.</l>
<l>If you provide for those in [your] service in the blooming world,</l>
<l>with knowledge that does not become blunt as a weapon, your glowing light will not vanish.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
